{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/headercrop.gif?t=1736959698\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/ENG_BannerText_History_resize.png?t=1736959698\" /><br>In the old castle of the renowned inventor Heinrich Von Schinker, in northern England, Heinrich's spirit returns as a small ghost.<br><br>Alongside a mysterious bubble that he can move with gentle blows, he must face his own out-of-control inventions and fierce wild animals.<br><br>Guiding the bubble to freedom is his only goal.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/encuentro.gif?t=1736959698\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/ENG_BannerText_Game_resize.png?t=1736959698\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Challenge Your Skills</strong></h2>Overcome levels filled with dangers and puzzles that will test your abilities. With addictive gameplay and devilish difficulty, your only goal is to protect the bubble at all costs.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/gameplay1.gif?t=1736959698\" /><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Defeat Epic Bosses</strong></h2>Face fierce bosses that will make you sweat. Only the most skilled will emerge victorious.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/bosses.gif?t=1736959698\" /><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Relive the Original Classic</strong></h2>Enjoy the full remaster of the 90s game, with 36 original levels recreated with completely renewed art.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/retro.gif?t=1736959698\" /><br></li><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Compete for Glory</strong></h2>Perfect your times in speedrun mode and submit your results online to secure your place in the prestigious Hall of Fame.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/speedrun.gif?t=1736959698\" /></li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/ENG_BannerText_Info_resize.png?t=1736959698\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Enjoy an adventure with over 40 levels filled with skill and clever puzzles.<br></li><li> Three difficulty levels tailored to your playstyle.<br></li><li> Completely revamped graphics and sound that bring the magical world of the castle to life.<br></li><li> Dive deep into Heinrich's story by finding hidden collectibles throughout the castle chambers.<br></li><li> Upload your scores and compare them with the best players worldwide in the online ranking.<br></li><li> Discover secret rooms, alternative endings, and unlock challenging in-game achievements.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/bat.gif?t=1736959698\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/extras/separador.png?t=1736959698\" /></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736959698","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/page.bg.jpg?t=1736959698","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/75a5efb8a3d230f621ae9bcfce47aa727a507177/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736959698","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412240/75a5efb8a3d230f621ae9bcfce47aa727a507177/capsule_184x69.jpg?t